task_prompt: My week of Jan 20-24, 2025 is extremely packed with meetings. I desperately need 6 one-hour deep work blocks squeezed into whatever gaps exist. Find slots that don't overlap with any existing meetings. Please ensure at least 15 minutes of travel time on each side of every block. Working hours are 9am-5pm UTC. Be very careful with the timing - some gaps may look like an hour but are actually shorter. It's OK if some days have no focus blocks and others have two.

custom_rules.description: 15-min travel time buffer between focus blocks and other events
